hadiths[102]{hadithnumber,text}:
4494,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Qureza aur Nazeer (yahood ke do qabiley they) aur Nazeer Qureza ki bih nisbat ziyada moazzaz tha. to jab Qureza ka koi aadmi nazeer ke kisi aadmi ko qatl kar deta to usey uskey badley mein qatl kar diya jata tha. aur jab nazeer ka koi aadmi Qureza ke aadmi ko qatl kar deta to (maqtool ke waarison ko) eik sau wasq khajoor diyat deta tha. phir jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  bhejey gaey to nazeer ke aadmi ne Qureza ke eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya. to Qureza ne kaha : qatil hamarey hawaley karo ham usey qatl karengey . nazeer ne kaha : hamarey tumharey darmiyan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazi aur hakam hain. to wo log aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye . to ye aayaat nazil huin (وَإِنْ حَكَمْتَ فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ بِالْقِسْطِ) ''aap agar faisla farmaeyn to in mein insaf se faisla farmaeyn.''  is mein (القسط) ''insaf'' ka mafhoom ''jaan ke badley jaan'' hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Qureza aur nazeer dono Hazrat Harun Alehissalam ki nasal se hain.
4495,"Hazrat Abu-Ramsa (Rifa bin Yasrabi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke main apney walid ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir hua. aapney merey walid se puchha : ''ye tumhara beta hai?'' (walid ne) kaha : haan , rabe-Kaaba ki qasam ! aapney farmaya : ''sach?'' merey baap ne kaha : main iski gawahi deta hun. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hanstay huey tabassum farmaya , kyonkey meri mushaabihat merey baap mein numaya thi aur baap ne merey baarey mein qasam khai thi. phir aapney farmaya : ''khabrdar ! na ye terey kisi qusur mein pakda jaeyga aur na to iskey badley mein.'' phir aapney ye aayat padhi :( وَلَا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌ وِزْرَ أُخْرَى ) ''koi jaan kisi jaan ka bojh na uthaeygi.''"
4496,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Khuzaae riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi ka koi qatl ho gaya ho ya uska koi uzu kat gaya ho to usey teen mein se eik ka ikhtiyar hai : ya to qisaas (badla) ley ya maaf kar dey ya diyat le-ley , aur jo koi chauthi baat chahey to uskey haath pakad lo, aur jo koi iskey baad ziyadti karey to uskey liye dard naak azab hai.''"
4497,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : maine dekha hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jab bhi koi aisa muqadma laya jata jis mein qisaas hota to aap maaf karney ka farmatey.
4498,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik aadmi qatl ho gaya aur uska muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney pesh kiya gaya to aapney qatil ko maqtool ke waris ke hawaley kar diya. qatil ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qasam ! maine uskey qatl ka irada nahin kiya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey waris se farmaya : ''khabrdar ! agar ye sachcha hua phir to ne usko qatl kar diya to, to jahannam mein jaeyga.'' chunanche usney usko chhod diya. raawi ne bataya ke wo qatil chamdey ki eik lambi patti se bandhaa hua tha, chunanche wo apni patti ko ghaseet'taa hua chala gaya aur phir uska naam hi (ذوالنسعة) (patti wala) pad gaya."
4499,Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik qatil laya gaya uski gardan mein chamdey ki eik patti (bandhi hui) thi. aapney maqtool ke wali ko bulaya aur us se kaha : ''kya tum maaf kartey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya tum diyat lena qubul kartey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya qatl karogey ?'' usney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''jao usey ley jao.'' isliye jab usney pusht pheri to aapney (phir) puchha : ''kya maaf kartey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya diyat letey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney kaha : ''kya qatl karogey ?'' usney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''jao ley jao.'' phir chauthi baar farmaya : ''agar tum usko maaf kar do to ye apney aur apney maqtool dono ke gunah apney sar lega.'' raawi ne kaha : chunanche usney usko maaf kar diya. Waael kehtey hain ke maine qatil ko dekha ke wo apni patti ghasitey ja raha tha.
4500,Janab Alqama bin Waael ne ye riwayat apni sanad se aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat ki.
4501,"Janab Alqama bin Waael apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs eik Habshi ko pakdey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : isney merey bhatijey ko qatl kar dala hai. aapney puchha : ''tu ne usko kis tarah qatl kiya tha?'' usney bataya ke maine uskey sar par kulhaada maara tha, lekin usey mera qatl kerney ka irada nahin tha. aapney puchha : ''kya terey paas maal hai ke to uski diyat dey sakey?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya agar main tujhey chhod dun, aur to logon se maangey aur uski diyat jama kar ley (to kya aisey kar sakta hai?)'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya terey Malik (ya teri qom waley ( tujhey uski diyat dey saktey hain ?'' usney kaha : nahin. to aapney maqtool ke wali se kaha : ''usko pakad ley.'' chunanche wo usey qatl kerney ke liye ley chala, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! agar isney usko qatl kar diya to usi ki manind ho jaeyga.'' to wo (maqtool ka wali) qatil ko lekar us jagah pahunch gaya jahan se usney aap ki baat suni thi aur bola : lijiye ! ye raha aur jo chahen iskey mutalliq hukm farmaeyn . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isko chhod do, ye apney aur apney maqtool ke gunah apney sar lekar jahannamiyon mein se hoga .'' Hazrat Waael ne kaha : chunanche usney usko chhod diya."
4502,"Janab Abu-Umama bin Sehal bayan kartey hain ke ham Saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey jabkey wo apney ghar mein mahsoor they. ghar main eik aisi jagah thi ke jo wahan dakhil hota maqame-balaat par baithey logon ki baaten sun sakta tha. chunanche Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) us jagah mein gaey aur phir hamarey paas wapis aaye to unka rang uda hua tha. unhoney bataya ke ye (bulwaai) ab mujhey qatl kar deney ki dhamki deney lagey hain. ham ne kaha : Ameerul-momeneen ! Shan Wala Allah unki janib se aap ki kifaayat kerega . unhoney kaha : ye mujhey kyon qatl karna chahtey hain? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''kisi musalman ka khoon halal nahin, siwaye uskey ke us se teen baaton mein se koi eik sadir ho : Islam ke baad kufr , shaadi shuda honey ke baad zina , ya qisaas ke baghair kisi ko qatl kar dena.'' aur Allah ki qasam ! maine kabhi zina nahin kiya, jahiliyat mein na Islam laney ke baad . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Saiyedna Usman aur Saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne daure jahiliyat hi se sharab chhod di thi."
4503,"Ziyad bin Saad bin Zameera Salma se manqul hai aur ye Wahab bin Bayan ki riwayat hai aur ziyada kamil hai. wo (Ziyad bin Saad) Urwa bin Zuber se apney walid ke wastey se riwayat bayan kartey hain. . . . aur Musa bin-Ismail ki sanad mein hai ke Ziyad ne apney walid se aur apney dada (Zameera) se riwayat kiya aur ye dono (Saad aur Zameera) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ladaai Hunain mein hazir they ham Wahab bin Bayan ki taraf laut'tey hain ke . . . . Mohlim bin Jassama Laisee ne qubul Islam ke baad qabeela ashja' ke eik aadmi ko qatl kar diya. aur ye diyat ka pehla muqadma tha jis ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya. chunanche Uena ne maqtool Ashjai ke baarey mein baat shuru ki kyonkey uska talluq qabeela ghatfaan se tha aur Aqraa bin Haabis ne Mohlim ki janib se baat ki kyonkey wo qabeela khandaf se tha. un logon ki aawazen oonchi ho gaeen aur bahut shor-ghul aur jhagda hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Uena ! kya tum diyat qubul nahin kartey ho?'' Uena ne kaha : nahin, Allah ki qasam ! jab tak main uski aurton ko bhi wohi dukh aur aziyat na pahuncha lun jo usney meri aurton ko pahunchaya hai. phir aawazen oonchi ho gaeen , bada shor-ghul aur jhagda hua , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Uena ! kya tum diyat qubul nahin kartey ho?'' to Uena ne pehley ki tarah jawab diya. yahan tak ke bano Leis ka eik aadmi khada hua jis ka naam Mukaitil tha. wo hathiyar band tha aur dhaal uskey haath mein thi. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey us waqiey mein jo ibtadaaey Islam mein roonumaa hua (saamne aaya) hai, aur koi misal nahin milti ke ghaat par aati bakriyon mein pehli ko pathar maar diya jaey to aakhiri bhi bhag jati hai. aur (doosri misal) aaj eik tariqa ikhtiyar karo to kal usey badal do. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pachas oont to fori taur par abhi adaa hon aur pachas jab ham Madina lauten.'' aur ye waqia aap ke safar ka hai. (sahibe-maamla) Mohlim eik daraz qad gehun-goon aadmi tha, wo logon ki eik janib mein baitha hua tha. log usi haalat par they ke wo jagah banata hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney aa baitha , jabkey uski aakhon se aansu jari they. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujh se ye kaam ho gaya jiski aap ko khabar mili hai, main Allah ke huzur tauba karta hun. Allah ke Rasool ! merey liye Allah se istighfar farmaeyn . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to ne Islam latey hi apney hathiyar se qatl kar dala . aey Allah ! Mohlim ki bakhshish na farma.'' ye aapney buland aawaz se kaha. Abu-Salma ne mazeed kaha : phir wo uth khada hua aur apni chadar ke pallu se apney aansu poonchh raha tha. ibne Is-haq kehtey hain : uski qom ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baad mein uskey liye istighfar farmaya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Nazar bin Shumeil ne (الغير) ka mafhoom ''diyat'' bataya hai."
4504,"Janab Abu-Shuraih ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey bano khuza'aa ! tum ne huzail ka ye aadmi qatl kiya hai, main uski diyat ada karta hun, meri is baat ke baad jis kisi ka koi aadmi qatl kiya gaya to uskey warison ko do baaton mein se eik ka ikhtiyar hoga ke ya to diyat ley lein ya (qisaas mein) qatl keren.''"
4505,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke jab Makka Fateh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmaya : ''jis kisi ka koi aadmi qatl kiya gaya ho to usey do baaton mein se eik ka ikhtiyar hai ke ya to diyat diya jaey ya qisaas.'' tab ehale-Yamen mein se eik aadmi khada hua uska naam Abu-Shah tha, usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey ye likh dijiye. (Abbas bin Waleed ke alfaz hain.  (اكتبوا لي)) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Shah ko likh do.'' hadees ke ye alfaz Ahmed bin Ibrahim ke hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is se murad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khutbe ka likhna hai."
4506,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi momin ko kafir ke badley qatl na kiya jaey aur jisney kisi momin ko jaan bojh kar qatl kya to qatil ko maqtool ke warison ke hawala kiya jaey, wo chahen to usey (qisaas mein) qatl kar den aur agar chahen to diyat ley lein.''"
4507,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney diyat leney ke baad qatl kiya main usey nahin chhodunga.''"
4508,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik yahudi aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas zahar aalud bakri (ka gosht) laee to aapney us se khaya . phir us aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya , aapney us se uskey mutalliq puchha to usney kaha : maine aap ko qatl karna chaha tha. to aapney farmaya : ''Allah tujhey ye kaam na karney dega.'' ya farmaya : ''Allah tujhey mujh par musallat na honey dega.'' Sahaba ne kaha : kya ham isey qatl na kar den? aapney farmaya : ''nahin.'' Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main us zahar ka asar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke halaq mein kowey par dekhta raha."
4509,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik yahudi aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko zahar aalud bakri hadiya ki . Hazrat Abu-Huraira ne kaha : phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usse koi ta'ruz (chhed-chhad) nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye yahudi aurat marhab ki behan thi jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko zahar deney ki koshish ki thi.
4510,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey they ke ehale khaibar ki eik yahudi aurat ne eik bakri ko aag par bhoon kar zahar aalud kiya aur phir usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hadiya dey diya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski dasti ka hissa liya aur khaney lagey aur aap ke sath aap ke Sahaba kiram ki eik jamaat bhi us se khaney lagi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney haath khinch lo. aur us aurat ko bulwaya aur us se puchha : ''kya to ne is bakri ko zahar aalud kiya hai? '' wo yahoodan boli : aap ko kis ne bataya hai? aapney farmaya : ''mujhey is dasti ne bataya hai jo merey haath mein hai. aurat ne kaha : haan . aapney puchha : ''tera is se kya irada tha?'' kehney lagi , maine kaha : agar ye Nabi hua to usey ye hergiz nuqsan nahin deygi aur agar Nabi na hua to ham is se rahat pa jaeyngey . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko maaf kar diya aur koi saza na di. aur aap ke wo Sahaba jinhon ne us bakri mein se khaya tha un mein se eik ( Bishr bin Bara bin Ma'roor) wafat pa gaey aur (khud) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey khaney ki wajeh se apney kandhon ke darmiyan mein pachhney lagwaaey. ye pachhney aap ko Abu Hind ne gaey ke seeng aur chhuri ke sath lagaey. aur Abu Hind ansaar ke qabeele bani biyaaza ka ghulam tha."
4511,Hazrat Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke khaibar main eik yahudi aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik bhuni hui bakri hadiya ki . . . . aur Hazrat Jabir ki riwayat ki manind riwayat kiya. . . . kaha ke phir Hazrat Bishr bin Bara bin Ma'roor Ansari (us ki wajeh sey) faut ho gaey. to aapney us yahoodan ko bulwaya (aur us se puchha :  )  ''tujhey is kaam par kis chiz ne aamada kiya tha?'' . . . . to hadees Jabir ki manind zikr kiya. . . . tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey qatl kar diya gaya. aur pachhney lagwaaney ka maamla is mein zikr nahin kiya.
4512,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hadiya qubul farma letey they aur sadqa na khaya kartey they. Hazrat Abu-Salma se riwayat hai, . . aur Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka wastey zikr nahin kiya. . . . kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hadiya qubul farma letey aur sadqa nahin khaya kartey they. mazeed kaha ke eik yahudi aurat ne khaibar mein aap ko eik bakri hadiya ki jo bhooni gaee thi aur usney usey zahar aalud kar diya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sath logon (Sahaba kiraam) ne bhi us se khaya. aapney farmaya : ''apney haath khinch lo, isney mujhey bataya hai ke ye zahar aalud hai.'' phir (us ki wajeh sey) Bishr bin Bara bin Ma'roor Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey . to aapney us yahoodan ko bulwaya (aur puchha : ( ''tujhey is kaaristaani par kis chiz ne aamada kiya tha?'' usney kaha : agar aap Nabi hain to merey is kaam se aap ka koi nuqsan nahin hoga. aur agar aap badshah hain to main logon ko aap se rahat pahuncha sakoongi. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey qatl kar diya gaya. phir aapney apni us takleef ke mutalliq bataya jis mein aap ki wafat hui thi : ''main un luqmon ki wajeh se jo maine khaibar mein khaye they hamesha takleef mein raha hun, aur ab ye waqt aa gaya hai ke usney meri shaah rag kaat di hai."
4513,"Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke jis bimari mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui un dino main Umme-Mubashshir (Zauja (biwi) Zaid bin Harisa) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kya guman kartey hain? main apney bete ke mutalliq yehi samajhti hun ke wo zahar aalud bakri jo usney aap ke sath khaibar mein khai thi wo usi se mutassir hua tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bhi apney mutalliq usi ka guman hai aur ye waqt aa gaya hai ke meri shaah ragein kat rahi hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Imam Abdur-Razzaaq (Rahimahullah) ne ye riwayat kaee baar ba-sand Maamer Zohri ke wastey , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal , aur kaee baar Zohri ne Abdur-Rehman bin ka'ab bin Malik ke wastey se mausool riwayat ki hai. Abdur-Razzaaq (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Maamer jab ye riwayat mursal bayan kartey to ham usi tarah likh letey they aur jab musnad riwayat kartey to ham usi tarah likh letey aur hamarey nazdik ye sab sahih hain. Abdur-Razzaaq ne bataya ke jab ibne Mubarak Maamer ke yahan gaey to unhoney wo tamam ahadis jo wo moquf bayan kiya kartey they ibne-Mubarak ko musnad riwayat keen."
4514,Hazrat Umme-Mubashshir (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur Mukhlid bin Khalid (ki mazkura baala riwayat) ke ham-maani bayan kiya. jaisey ke hadees Jabir mein aaya hai. . . unhoney kaha ke phir Hazrat Bishr bin Bara bin Ma'roor (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us yahudi aurat ko bulwaya aur us se puchha ke tujhey is kaaristaani par kis chiz ne aamada kiya? . . . . aur hadees Jabir ki manind riwayat kiya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya aur usey qatl kar diya gaya aur pachhney lagwaaney ka zikr nahin kiya.
4515,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney ghulam ko qatl kerega ham usey qatl karengey aur jo apney ghulam ki naak kaatey ga ham uski naak kaateingey .''"
4516,"Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala riwayat ke jaisi riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney apney ghulam ko khassi kiya ham usey khassi kar dengey.'' aur phir Shoba aur Hammad ki hadees ki jaisi riwayat kiya. (yani jo ooper mazkur hui hai.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke isey Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne ba-waaste Hisham riwayat kiya aur hadees ki hadees tarah bayan kiya."
4517,Janab Qatada ne ba-sand Shoba mazkura baala (oopar zikr ki gaee) riwayat ki jaisi riwayat kiya. mazeed kaha ke phir Hasan ye hadees bhool gaey aur kaha kartey they ke kisi azad ko kisi ghulam ke badley mein qatl nahin kiya jaeyga.
4518,"Hisham ne ba-waasta Qatada , Hasan se riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha ke azad se ghulam ka qisaas nahin liya jata."
4519,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi chalata hua Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : uski londi thi , aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''afsos tujh par , tujhey kya hua hai?'' usney kaha : bahut bura hua hai. maine apney Malik ki londi ko dekh liya, to usey ghairat aai aur phir usney mera zikr (khas ang) kaat dala hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us aadmi ko merey paas lao.'' usey dhoondaa gaya magar na la sakey. to aapney ghulam se farmaya : ''jao tum azad ho.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( agar wo mujhey dobara ghulam bananey ki koshish karey to) meri madad kon kerega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har musalman.'' ya farmaya : ''har momin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke azad kiye janey waley ka naam Rooh bin Dinar tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : jisney uska zikr (ang) kaataa uska naam Zanbaa'a tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ye Zanbaa'a Abu-Rooh hai. ye us ghulam (Rooh bin Dinar) ka aaqa tha."
4520,"Hazrat Sehal bin Abu-Hasma aur Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Mahisa bin Masood aur Abdullah bin Sehal khaibar ki janib rawana huey aur khajuron ke baaghaat mein juda-juda ho gaey. isliye Abdullah bin Sehal ko qatl kar diya gaya. so unhoney (wahan ke) yahudiyon par ilzam lagaya. phir us (maqtool) ka bhai Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal aur uskey chacha zaad Huwesa aur Mahisa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir huey. Abdur-Rehman apney bhai ke maamley mein baat karney laga jabkey wo un sab se chhota tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''badey ko baat kerney do.'' ya farmaya :  ''pehley bada baat shuru karey.'' phir un dono ne apney bhai ke baarey mein baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se pachas aadmi unke kisi ke khilaf pachas qasmen khaeyn to us mulzim ki rassi tumharey hawaley kar di jaeygi.'' unhoney kaha : ye aisa maamla hai jo ham ne apni aakhon se nahin dekha to ham qasmen kaisey khaeyn? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir yahudi pachas qasmen de-kar tum se bari ho jaeyngey.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye kafir log hain. (unki qasmon ka kya aetbar?) gharz ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se uski diyat ada farmaee. Sehal kehtey hain : main eik din unke baadey mein chala gaya to un oontniyon mein se eik ne mujhey laat dey maari . Hammad bin Zaid ne yehi ya uskey qarib qarib bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Bishr bin Mufazzal aur Malik ne Yahya bin Saeed se naqal kiya aur kaha : ''kya tum log pachas qasmen khaogey ke apney aziz ke khoon ke haq-daar bin sako? ya qatil ke haqdaar bin sako?'' Bishr ne ''khoon ke haqdaar banney '' ka zikr nahin kiya. aur Abda ne ba-waaste Yahya wohi kaha hai jaisey ke Hammad ne kaha . aur ibne-Uena ki riwayat jo Yahya se hai us mein usney ibtidaai (shuruati) taur par yun kaha hai : ''yahudi pachas qasmen kha kar tum se bari ho jaeyngey.'' aur ''haqdaar banney'' ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye ibne-Uena ka weham hai."
4521,"Hazrat Sehal bin Abu-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) aur unki qom ke badon ne khabar di ke Abdullah bin Sehal aur Muhesa logon ko maali mushkilat ka samna tha to wo dono (mehnat mazduri ki talash mein) khaibar ki taraf nikal gaey . phir Muhesa ko khabar di gaee ke Abdullah bin Sehal ko qatl karkey eik kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. to wo yahudiyon ke paas gaya aur kaha : Allah ki qasam ! tum logon hi ne isko qatl kiya hai. unhoney jawab diya : Allah ki qasam ! ham ne isko qatl nahin kiya. phir wo chala aaya aur apni qom ke paas pahuncha aur unko sab bataya . to wo aur uska bada bhai Huwesa aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein) hazir huey. to Muhesa baat kerney laga . . . . aur yehi tha jo khaibar mein gaya tha. . . . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''badey ka khayal kar.'' yani jo umr mein bada hai. phir Huwesa ne baat ki . phir Muhesa ne ki . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo log tumharey aadmi ki ya to diyat dengey warna jang ke liye tayyar rahen.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ye tafsil likh bheji . unhoney jawaaban likha : Allah ki qasam ! ham ne usey qatl nahin kiya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Huwesa , Muhesa aur Abdur-Rehman se farmaya : ''kya tum log qasmen khao gey ke apney aadmi ke khoon ke haqdaar bin sako.'' unhoney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''phir tumharey muqabley mein yahudi qasmen khaeyn gey.'' un logon ne kaha : wo to musalman nahin hain. (yani unki qasmon ka kyonkar aetbar keren?) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se uski diyat ada farmaee aur sau oontniyaan unki taraf bhej dein yahan tak ke unke ehatey mein dakhil kar di gaeen. Sehal kehtey hain ke un mein se eik surkh oontni ne mujhey laat dey maari thi."
4522,Janab Amr bin Shuaib riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Nasar bin Malik ke eik aadmi ko qasamat ke faisley ki bina par (qisaas mein) qatl kiya tha. ye qabeela (taaif ke muzaafat mein) لیہ shehar ke kinarey بحرۃ الرغاء ke maqam par sakunat pazeer tha. raawi ne kaha ke qatil aur maqtool un mein se they. ye alfaz Mehmood bin Khalid ke hain. jisney wazahat se (بحرۃ الرغاء) aur (شط لیہ) ke alfaz bayan kiye hain.
4523,Janab Sehal bin Abu-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unki qom ke kuch log Khaibar gaey aur wahan ja kar alehda-alehda ho gaey . phir unhoney apney mein se eik ko paya ke usey qatl kar diya gaya tha to unhoney wahan ke logon se kaha jahan qatl hua tha ke tum ne hamarey sathi ko qatl kya hai. unhoney kaha : ham ne usko qatl nahin kya aur na hamen uskey qatil ki khabar hai. chunanche ham Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aagey. to aapney farmaya : ''tum log uskey qatil ke mutalliq gawah pesh karo.'' unhoney kaha : hamarey paas koi gawah nahin hai. aapney farmaya : ''tab wo tumharey jawab mein qasmen khaeyngey?'' unhoney kaha : ham yahudiyon ki qasmon par razi nahin hain. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne napasand kya ke us maqtool ka khoon zaya jaey to sadqey ke oonton mein se uski diyat so oontniyaan ada farma di.
4524,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Ansariyon ka eik aadmi khaibar mein qatl ho gaya. to uskey waris Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan gaey aur us maqtool ka zikr kiya. aapney farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas do gawah hain jo tumharey us sathi ke qatl ke mutalliq gawahi den?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wahan musalmanon mein se koi bhi na tha, aur wo log yahudi hain, wo is se bhi badi baaton ki jur'at kar saktey hain. aapney farmaya : ''to un mein se pachas aadmiyon ko muntakhab kar lo aur un se qasmen ley lo.'' magar unhoney inkar kar diya. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se uski diyat ada farmaee."
4525,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Bujeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! beshak Sehal ko is hadees (ke bayan kerney) mein weham hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahood ko ye likha tha ke bila-shuba tum mein maqtool paya gaya hai, lihaza uski diyat ada karo. to unhoney likha aur (apni tehreer mein) Allah ke naam ki pachas qasmen khaeen ke ham ne usko qatl nahin kiya aur na hamein qatil ka koi ilm hai. unhoney kaha : isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski diyat eik sau oontniyaan apni taraf se ada farma di."
4526,"Janab Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman aur Sulaiman bin Yasar , Ansaar ke kaee logon se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahudiyon se kaha . . . . aur un hi se ibtida (shuruat) ki . . . . ''tum mein se pachas aadmi qasmen khaeyn.''  magar unhoney inkar kar diya. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ansariyon se kaha ke apna haq (qasmen kha kar) Sabit karo. to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham an-dekhi baat par kaisey qasmen khaeyn? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski diyat yahudiyon par dal-di kyonkey wo maqtool un hi ke yahan paya gaya tha."
4527,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik ladki paaee gaee ke uska sar do pattharon mein rakh kar kuchal diya gaya tha (aur abhi us mein zindagi ki ramaq baqi thi) to us se puchha gaya : ye terey sath kis ne kiya hai? kya falan ne? kya falan ne? yahan tak ke eik yahudi ka naam liya gaya to usney apney sar se ishara kiya. (haan) to us yahudi ko pakda gaya aur phir usney aetraaf kar liya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke uska sar bhi pattharon se kuchla jaey.
4528,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik yahudi ne eik Ansari ladki ko qatl kar diya jo kuchh zewar pehney huey thi , aur phir eik kunwen mein phenk diya aur uska sar patthar se kuchal diya. phir usey pakad liya gaya to usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya to aapney uskey mutalliq hukm diya ke usey sangsaar kiya jaey yahan tak ke mar jaey. chunanche usey sangsaar kiya gaya , yahan tak ke wo mar gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne-Juraij ne Ayub se usi ki manind riwayat kiya hai."
4529,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik ladki apney chaandi ke zewar pehney huey thi ke eik yahudi ne patthar se uska sar kuchal diya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us ladki ke paas aaye jabke (abhi) us mein zindagi ki ramaq baqi thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''tujhey kis ne qatl kiya hai? kya falan ne qatl kiya hai? '' usney apney sar se ishara kiya nahin. aapney puchha : ''tujhey kis ne qatl kiya hai, kya falan ne qatl kiya hai?'' usney apney sar se ishara kiya : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya falan ne tujhey qatl kiya hai? '' usney apney sar se ishara kiya : haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm diya to usey do patharon mein rakh kar qatl kiya gaya."
4530,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main aur Ashtar Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey aur un se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aap ko koi khas wasiyat farmaee hai jo aam logon se na kahi ho? unhoney farmaya : nahin. siwaye iskey jo merey paas is maktoob (khat) mein hai. . . Musaddad kehtey hain ke phir unhoney wo tehreer nikali . Ahmed bin Hanbal ne kaha : unhoney apni talwaar ki miyaan mein se wo tehreer nikali . . . . to us mein tha : ''tamam ahle-eman ke khoon barabar hain aur wo apney alawa ke muqabley main eik haath hain (eik doosrey ki madad kerney ke paband hain.) unke zimmey aur amaan ka unka adnaa se adnaa aadmi bhi paband hai. khabrdar ! kisi momin ko kisi kafir ke badley mein aur kisi amaan waley ko uskey ayyaame amaan mein qatl na kiya jaey, jisney deen mein koi naya kaam kiya (bidat ejaad ki) to uska wabal uski apni jaan par hai, jisney koi bidat ejaad ki ya kisi bid'ati ko jagah di to us par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam logon ki lanat ho. Musaddad ne ba-waaste  ibn Abu-Arooba (yun) riwayat kiya : phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo tehreer nikali."
4531,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . . . aur mazkura baala riwayat Ali ki manind zikr kiya. is mein izafa hai : ''unka (musalmanon ka ( baeed (door) tareen fard bhi amaan dey sakta hai. aur unka mota-taaza aur qawi raftaar apney zaeef aur sust raftaar ko bhi sath milaaey (maale ghanimat mein usko shareek karey) aur chhotey dastey mein janey wala badey lashkar mein reh janey walon ko bhi shareek samjhey.''"
4532,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar koi shakhs apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekhay to kya usey qatl kar daley? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) boley : kyon nahin, qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath izzat di ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney sardar ki baat suno , kya keh raha hai. abdul-wahaab ki riwayat mein hai : ''suno Saad kya keh raha hai.'' (yani bahut hi ghairat mand hain.)"
4533,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : farmaiye ke agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair aadmi ko paon to kya usey chhod dun yahan tak ke chaar gawah laun? aapney farmaya : ''haan.''
4534,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Jahm bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko Zakat ka aamil bana kar bheja . sadqey (ke hisab) mein unka eik aadmi se jhagda ho gaya to Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko maara aur zakhmi kar diya. to wo log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chaley aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham badla lengey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham tumhen is is qadr maal detey hain.'' magar wo razi na huey. aapney farmaya : ''chalo is is qadr ley lo.'' wo razi na huey . aapney farmaya : ''is is qadr ley lo.'' to wo razi ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj shaam mein khutba dun-ga aur logon ko bataun-ga ke tum log razi ho gaey ho.'' unhoney kaha : theek hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba diya aur farmaya : ''banu Leis ke ye log merey paas qisaas ka mutalba lekar aaye they to maine unhen is is qadr maal ki pesh kash ki hai to wo razi ho gaey hain. (phir aap bano Leis se mukhatib huey) kya tum razamand ho?'' unhoney kaha : nahin. us par muhajrin bhuna uthey . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen unse baaz rakha to wo ruk gaey . aapney un logon ko phir bulaya aur mazeed maal ki peshkash ki aur un se puchha : ''kya tum razi ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''main logon ko khutba dunga aur unhen tumhari razamandi ka bataunga.'' unhoney kaha : theek hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba diya aur (un sey) puchha : ''kya tum razi ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan (ham razi hain).
4535,"Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik ladki paaee gaee jis ka sar do pattharon mein rakh kar kuchal diya gaya tha. to us se puchha gaya : terey sath ye kis ne kiya hai? kya falan ne , kya falan ne? yahan tak ke eik yahudi ka naam liya gaya to usney apney sar ke sath ishara kiya (ke haan ). wo yahudi pakad liya gaya to usney iqrar kar liya . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke uska sar bhi patthar se kuchla jaey."
4536,"Saiyedna Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : eik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuchh taqseem kar rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya aur aap ke ooper jhuk gaya , to aapney apni khajoor ki lathi se jo aap ke paas thi usey kachoka diya, isliye usse uska chehra zakhmi ho gaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usse farmaya : ''aao aur apna badla ley lo .'' usney jawab diya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine maaf kiya."
4537,"Janab Abu-Faraas ( Rabeea bIn Ziyad bin Anas Haarisi) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya aur kaha : main apney ummaal (governors) isliye nahin bhejta ke tumharey jismon par maaren ya tumharey maal tum se chheen lein. agar kisi ke sath aisa ho to usey chahiye ke apna muqadma merey paas laye taake main usse qisaas lun. to Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : agar kisi ne apni riaayaa mein se kisi ki taadeeb ki ho (usey saza di ho) to kya aap uska badla lengey? farmaya : haan , qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main us-se badla lunga. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke wo apni zaat se badla dilwatay they."
4538,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladaai karney (qisaas ka mutalba karney) waley badla leney mein hausle se kaam lein. (jaldi na karen) warison mein se maaf kerney ka haq darja badarja hai, chahey koi aurat hi ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ( ينحجزوا (ke maani hain : ''qisaas leney se ruk jana. mazeed farmatey hain ke mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke qatl ke maamley mein warison mein agar koi aurat bhi ho to wo bhi maaf kar sakti hai. aur) أن ينحجزوا (ke maani ke silsiley mein Abu-Ubaida se mujhey ye bayan kiya gaya hai ke uska mafhoom hai : ''qisaas leney se baaz rahen.''"
4539,"Janab Taaus (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke jo koi kisi balwe mein maara gaya ho. aur ibne Ubaid ki riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi balwe mein maara gaya ho (ke uska qatil dekha na gaya ho) sangbaari hui ho ya dandey bazi ya kisi lathi se mara ho to ye qatl khata hai, uski diyat qatl khata wali hogi . albatta jo shakhs (jaan boojh kar) amadan qatl kiya gaya ho to is mein qisaas hai. ibne Ubaid ke lafz hain (قود يد) (qatil ki jaan se qisaas liya jaeyga). aur jo us (qisaas leney) mein rukawat baney to us par Allah ki lanat aur ghazab ho, uska koi nafl ya farz maqbool nahin.'' Sufiyan ki hadees ziyada kamil hai."
4540,"Janab Taaus ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . . . aur mazkura baala riwayat Sufiyan ki manind bayan ki."
4541,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke jo shakhs ghalati se qatl kiya gaya ho to uski diyat eik sau oont hai. tees oontniyaan muannas eik saala , tees oontniyaan muannas do saala , tees oontniyaan muannas teen saala aur das adad oont muzakkir do saala."
4542,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein diyat ki qeemat aath sau Dinar (soney ke) ya aath hazar dirham (chaandi ke) thi aur un dino ehle-kitab ki diyat musalmanon ki diyat ke muqabley mein aadhi hoti thi. chunanche maamla aisey hi raha yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney. to unhoney khutba diya aur kaha : bila-shuba oont mahnge ho gaey hain, phir aapney ye diyat soney walon par eik hazar Dinar aur chaandi walon par baara hazar Dinar kar di , gaey walon ke liye do-sau gaey aur bakriyon walon ke liye do hazar bakriyan, hulley (khaas qism ke kapdey) tayyar kerney walon ke liye do-sau hulley muqarrar ki, aur zimmi logon ki diyat waisey hi rehney di aur usey nahin badhaya."
4543,"Janab Ata bin abi Ribah (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne diyat ki sharah yun muqarrar farmaee thi ke oonton walon par eik sau-oont, gaey walon par do-sau gaey, bakriyon walon par do-hazar bakriyan, hulley walon par do-sau hulley aur gehun walon par bhi kuchh muqarrar ki thi jo Muhammad bin Is-haq ko yaad nahin rahi."
4544,Janab Ata ( Ata bin abi Ribah ( ne Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( diyat ki sharah) muqarrar ki aur mazkura baala hadees Musa bin-Ismail ki manind riwayat ki . aur kaha ke ghalley walon par bhi kuch muqarrar ki thi jo mujhey yaad nahin.
4545,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qatle-khata ki diyat bees oontniyaan teen saala , bees oontniyaan chaar saala , bees oontniyaan eik saala , bees oontniyaan do saala aur bees oont  eik saala .'' aur Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol bhi yehi hai."
4546,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke bano Adi ka eik aadmi qatl ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski diyat baara hazar ( dirham ( tey farmaai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne-Uena ne b-waasta Amr , Ikrima sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kya magar us mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka wastey zikr nahin kya."
4547,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din khutba diya aur teen baar ''Allahu-akbar''kaha. phir farmaya (لا إله إلا الله وحده ‘ صدق وعده ‘ ونصر عبده وهزم الأحزاب وحده)'' eik Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin, usney apna wada sacha kar dikhaya , apney bandey ki madad ki . aur us eik akeley hi ne tamam girohon ko paspa kar diya. . . .'' yahan tak ki riwayat mujhey Musaddad se yaad hai. phir Suleman bin Harab aur Musaddad dono riwayat kerney mein muttafiq hain. . . . farmaya : '' khabardar! jahiliyat mein zikr kiye janey waley tamam mafaakhir ya khoon aur maal ke mataalbaat merey paon taley raundey ja rahey hain. ( unki koi haisiyat nahin aur koi mutalba nahin hoga ( siwaye uskey jo hajiyon ko pani pilaney ki khidmat thi ya Baitullah ki khidmat ka sharf tha ( wo baqi rahega .'' ( phir farmaya : '' khabrdar ! qatle-khata jo amad ke mushabeh ho, jo saantey ya lathi ki maar se hua ho uski diyat so oont hai. un mein chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey peton mein bachey hon.'' aur Musaddad ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai."
4548,"Musa bin-Ismail ne bayan kya, unhoney kaha hamen Wuhaib ne Khalid se hadees bayan ki usi asnaad se aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kya."
4549,"Qasim bin Rabeea ne b-waasta Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din Baitullah ki seedhi par khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ibne-Uena ne pasand Ali bin Zaid , Qasim bin Rabeea sey, unhoney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kya hai. aur Ayub sakhtiyaan ne Qasim bin Rabeea sey, unhoney Abdullah bin Amr se Khalid ki hadees ki manind riwayat kya hai. aur Hammad bin Salma ne Ali bin Zaid ki sanad sey, Yaqoob sadoosi sey, unhoney Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya hai. Zaid aur Abu-Musa ka qol hadees nabwi aur riwayat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) jo aagey aa rahi hai) ke mutabiq hai."
4550,"Mujahid riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne shubha amad mein faisla kya tha ke tees oontniyaan teen saala , tees oontniyaan chaar saala aur chaalis oontniyaan jo hamila hon aur unki umr mein do daantaa yani chatey se lekar nawin saal mein shuru honey wali ke darmiyan hon."
4551,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai unhoney farmaya : shubha amad ki diyat mein oont teen qismon ke hon : tentis oontniyaan teen saala , tentis oontniyaan chaar saala aur chauntees oontniyaan chhe se no saala ke darmiyan hon aur) ye aakhiri ( sab hamila hon."
4552,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke qatle-khata mein diyat ke oont chaar tarah ke hon : pachchis oontniyaan teen saala , pachchis oontniyaan chaar saala , pachchis oontniyaan do saala aur pachchis oontniyaan eik saala hon."
4553,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke shubhe-amad ki diyat mein oonton ki tafsil ye hai ke pachchis oontniyaan teen saala , pachchis oontniyaan chaar saala , pachchis oontniyaan do saala aur pachchis oontniyaan eik saala hon."
4554,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke mughalliz diyat ki tafsil ye hai ke chaalis oontniyaan chaar saala aur hamila , tees oontniyaan teen saala aur tees oontniyaan do saala hon aur qatle-khata mein tees oontniyaan teen saala , tees oontniyaan do saala , bees oont do saala aur bees oontniyaan eik saala ."
4555,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab ne Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se diyat mughalliza mein mazkura baala ki tarah bayan kya.
4556,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ungliyan sab barabar hain. ( her eik ki diyat ( das das oont hai.''"
4557,"Hazrat ( Abu-Musa ( Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' ungliyan sab barabar hain.'' ( Masruq kehtey hain ( maine kaha : das das oont ? unhoney kaha : '' haan . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees Muhammad bin Jaafar ne Shoba sey, usney ghalib se riwayat ki to kaha : maine Masruq bin Aus se suna . aur Ismail ne riwayat ki to kaha : mujhey ghalib Tammar ne abu-Waleed ki sanad se bayan ki . aur Hanzala bin Abu-Safiya ne ghalib se Ismail ki sanad se bayan ki ."
4558,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aur ye barabar hain.'' yani angoothaa aur chhanguliyan ."
4559,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ungliyan sab barabar hain, daant sab barabar hain, aagey ke do daant aur daadhein , ye aur ye sab barabar hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat nazar bin Shumeil ne Shoba se (mazkura baala riwayat ( abdus-Samad ke ham-maani bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : hamen ( abu-Jaafar Ahmed bin Saeed ( Darmi ne nazar (bin Shumeil ( se ye hadees bayan ki ."
4560,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' daant sab barabar hain aur ungliyan ( sab ( barabar hain.''"
4561,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dono haath aur dono paon ki ungliyan , sab barabar qarar di hain."
4562,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya jabke aap apni kamar Kaaba se lagaey huey they : '' ungliyon mein das das oont hain.''
4563,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' daanton mein paanch paanch oont hain.''
4564,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qatl khata mein dehat walon par oonton ki qeemat ke aetbar se diyat laagoo kartey they, chaar so Dinar ya uskey barabar chaandi . jab oont mahnge ho jatey to aap diyat ki qeemat badha detey aur jab sastey ho jatey to diyat ki qeemat kam kar detey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ye qeemat chaar so Dinar se aath so Dinar tak ya uskey barabar aath hazar dirham rahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gaey walon par do so gayen laagu kin aur jiski diyat mein bakriyan aati thin to un par do hazar bakriyan muqarrar kin . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''diyat maqtool ke warison mein qurbat ke aetbar se wirsey mein taqseem hogi aur jo baqi bach rahey wo asabaat ke liye hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne naak ke baarey mein faisla farmaya ke jab puri tarah kaat di gaee ho, us mein puri diyat hai aur jab uska sira ( بانسہ ( kaataa gaya ho to us mein nisf diyat pachas oont ya uskey barabar sona ya chaandi ya eik so gaey ya eik hazar bakri hai. aur eik haath mein , jab wo kaat diya gaya ho, to us mein aadhi diyat hai. aur eik paon mein aadhi diyat hai. khopdi ka zakhm jo dimagh tak pahunchey , us mein tihai diyat hai, tentis oont aur eik oont ka tihai ya uski qeemat sona ya chaandi ya gayen ya bakriyan . aur jo zakhm pet mein lagey to us mein bhi usi tarah se hai. ( tihai diyat .) aur ungliyon mein , her ungli ke badley das oont hain. aur daanton mein her daant mein paanch oont hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke aurat ( agar koi jurm karey to us ( ki diyat uskey usba ke zimmey hai yani jo us hissey ke waris bantey hain jo muqarrara hisson ke baad baqi bach rahey (yani baap , beta , bhai aur chacha waghera .) aur agar aurat qatl ho jaey to uski diyat uskey warison mein taqseem hogi aur yehi log qatil se qisaas leney ke haqdaar hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qatil ke liye kuch nahin. aur agar maqtool ka aur koi waris na ho to sab se qarib tareen aadmi uska waris hoga aur qatil ko virasat mein se kuch nahin milega . Muhammad bin Rashid ne kaha : mujhey ye tamam riwayat Suleman bin Musa ne Amr bin Shuaib ki sanad key sath apney walid sey, usney apney dada sey, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Muhammad bin Rashid ehle dimashq se they aur qatl (ke khof ( se Basra bhag gaey they."
4565,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qatl shubhe amad ki diyat mughalliz ( saqeel aur shadeed ( hoti hai jaisey ke qatle-amad ki, magar uska murtakib qatl nahin kya ja sakta.  ( Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne ( kaha ke khaleel ne ibn Rashid se mazeed kaha : '' wo ( shubhe-amad ( yun hai ke shetan logon mein fasad paida kar dey aur balwe mein koi khoon ho jaey ( qatil ko kisi ne dekha na ho (aur ladaai kerney walon mein koi gahri dushmani bhi na ho aur na unhoney aslaha uthaya ho.''"
4566,Janab Amr bin Shuaib se marwi (bayan) hai ke unke walid ne unhen ( unke dada ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aisey zakhm jo haddi khol den un mein paanch paanch oont hain.''
4567,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aankh ki chot mein faisla farmaya ke aankh agar apni jagah qaaim rahey (aur beenai jati rahey) to us mein tihai diyat hai."
4568,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aurten bano huzail ke eik aadmi ki zojiyat mein thin . un mein se eik ne dusri ko khemey ka baans dey maara aur usey aur uskey pet ke bachey ko qatl kar diya. wo log apna jhagda Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley aaye . to dono atraaf ke logon mein se kisi eik ne kaha : kis tarah diyat den ham uski jo na roya na khaya , na piya na chillaya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (uskey andaze-guftgu par) farmaya : ''kya dehatiyon ki si sajaa hai.'' al-gharaz aapney farmaya (us bachchey ki diyat) eik ghulam hai aur usey qaatila ke warison ke zimmey lagaya ke wo ada karen."
4569,"Mansoor ne apni sanad se mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kya. aur mazeed kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqtoola aurat ki diyat qaatila ke warison ke zimmey dali aur uskey pet ke bachey ke badley main eik ghulam lazim kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke hukm ne b-waasta Mujahid , Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se usi tarah riwayat kya hai."
4570,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon se mashwara kya ke agar kisi aurat ke pet ka bacha saaqit kar diya gaya ho ( to us mein kya diyat ho?). Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us main eik ghulam ya londi deney ka faisla farmaya tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke koi gawah laiye jo aap ki taeed mein gawahi dey. chunanche wo Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ko ley aaye . Harun ne mazeed kaha : chunanche unhoney gawahi di yani agar koi pet wali aurat ko sadma pahunchaey ( to uski diyat yehi hai) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke abu-Ubaid se marwi (bayan) hai ke Isqaat ko) إملاص ( isliye kehtey hain ke aurat bachey ko qabl az waqt phisla deti hai. aur her wo chiz jo haath waghera se phisal jaey usey ( ملص ( kehtey hain.
4571,Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Hammad bin Zaid aur Hammad bin Salma ne Hisham bin Urwa se usney apney walid se riwayat kya ke beshak umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha . . . .
4572,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us faisley ke baarey mein puchha ( jo pet ke bachey ke baarey mein hua tha ( to hamal bin Malik bin naabgha utha aur kaha ke main do aurton ke darmiyan mein tha (meri do biwiyan thin ( to eik ne dusri ko khemey ka baans dey maara aur usko aur uskey pet ke bachey ko maar dala . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey bachchey ke baarey main eik ghulam ada kerney ka faisla kya aur us aurat ko) jo qaatila thi qisaas mein) qatl kerney ka faisla kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Nazar bin Shumeil ne kaha ke) mistah ( se murad wo lakdi hai jiskey zariey se tanur se roti nikali jati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : jabkey abu-Ubaid ne kaha ke) mistah ( khemey ki lakdi ko kehtey hain.
4573,"Janab Taaus kehtey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) member par khadey huey . . . . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya magar us mein '' us aurat ( qaatila (ke qatl kiye janey ka zikr nahin kya. '' albatta ( janeen ke badley mein) eik ghulam ya londi diye janey ka bayan kya. Taaus ne kaha, us par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allahu-akbar, agar main ye na sunta to uskey ilawa koi aur faisla kar bethta."
4574,"Janab Ikrima ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se hamal bin Malik ke waqia mein bayan kya ke usney aurat ka bacha saaqit kar diya jo murda tha aur uskey baal ug chukey they aur aurat bhi mar gaee. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski diyat us qaatila ke warison par dal di. maqtula ke chacha ne kaha : uska bacha saaqit hua hai, aey Allah ke Nabi , jiskey baal ug chukey they. to qaatila ke walid ne kaha : ye jhoota hai, Allah ki qasam! bachcha na cheekha na chillaya, na piya na khaya, aisa khoon to batil hota hai. (us mein qisaas hota hai na diyat.) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kya jahilon aur kaahinon ki si sajaa hai? bachey ki diyat main eik ghulam ya londi ada karo . Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain un aurton mein se eik ka naam Mulaika tha aur dusri ka Umme- Ghutef ."
4575,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke qabeela huzail ki do aurton mein se eik ne dusri ko qatl kar diya aur un dono mein se her eik ka shohar bhi tha aur bacha bhi . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqtoola ki diyat qaatila ke aaqila par dali. us qaatila ke shohar aur bete ko us diyat ki adaegi se bari rakha. to maqtoola ke aaqila kehney lagey ke uski meeras hamara haq hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin uski virasat uskey shohar aur bete ka haq hai.''
4576,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke qabeela huzail ki do aurten lad padin to eik ne dusri ko pathar dey maara aur usey qatl kar diya. chunanche wo apna maamla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke janeen ki diyat main eik ghulam ya londi ada ki jaey aur maqtoola ki diyat qaatila ke aaqila ke zimmey dali aur maqtoola ki virasat uskey bete aur uskey sath doosrey warison ko dilwai. to hamal bin Malik bin naabgha Hazli ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main bhala uska jurmaana kyonkar bharun jisney na piya na khaya, na bola na chillaya, aisa khoon to fuzul hota hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to kaahinon ka bhai lagta hai.'' aapney ye uski saji hui guftgu ki wajeh se farmaya."
4577,Janab ibn Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se us qissey mein riwayat kya ke phir wo aurat jis ko aapney ghulam ya londi dilwai faut ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla diya ke uski virasat uskey bete ko miley aur) qaatila ki taraf sey) diyat uskey usba ( aaqila ( par dali .
4578,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aurat ne dusri ko pathar dey maara , us se uska bacha saaqit ho gaya. pas ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney pesh kya gaya to aapney uskey bachey ke silsiley mein paanch so bakriyan zimmey lagaain aur us din se pathar maarney se mana farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke hadees mein riwayat to paanch so bakriyan hi hain, magar sahih ye hai ke so bakriyan thin . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke ye Abbas (bin Abdul-Azeem (ka weham hai."
4579,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janeen ke silsiley main eik ghulam ya londi ya eik ghoda ya khachar ada kerney ka faisla farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hammad bin Salma aur Khalid bin Abdullah ne Muhammad bin Amr se ye riwayat naqal ki hai magar un dono ne ghodey ya khachar ka zikr nahin kya.
4580,Janab Shobi se marwi (bayan) hai ke londi ghulam ki qeemat paanch so dirham hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain Rabeea ne kaha ke londi ghulam ki qeemat pachas Dinar hai.
4581,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne makatib, jo qatl kar diya jaey, ki diyat ke silsiley mein faisla farmaya ke wo jis qadr hissey apni kitaabat ka ada kar chuka ho us nisbat se azad aadmi ki diyat di jaey aur jis qadr baqi ho us mein ghulam ki diyat di jaey."
4582,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''makatib par jab koi had lazim aa rahi ho ya kisi ka waris bin raha ho to jis nisbat se azad ho chuka ho usi hisab se had laagu hogi ya virasat ka hissa paeyga . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain us riwayat ko Wuhaib ne Ayub ki sanad ke sath, Ikrima se unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya hai. aur Hammad bin Zaid aur Ismail ne b-waasta Ayub , Ikrima se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kya hai jabkey Ismail bin Uleh ne usey Ikrima ka qol banaya hai."
4583,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney daad se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ehad waley ( zimmi) ki diyat azad se aadhi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Usama bin Zaid Lesi aur Abdur-Rehman bin Haris ne Amr bin Shuaib se usi ki misl riwayat kya hai."
4584,"Hazrat Safwan apney walid Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : merey naukar ki eik shakhs se ladaai ho gaee to doosrey ne uskey haath par daanton se kaat liya to usney apna haath khinch liya us se uskey agley do daant toot gaey . to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chala gaya to aapney us (ke us nuqsan ( ko zaya qarar diya. aur farmaya : ''kya to chahta tha ke wo apna haath terey munh mein diye rehta aur to usey oont ki tarah chaba daalta?'' ( Abdul-Malik bin Abdul-Azeez bin juraij ne) kaha ke ibne-abi Mulaika ne apney dada se riwayat kya ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey zaya qarar diya aur kaha : door ho ( zaya hai) uska daant ."
4585,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya ne ye riwayat bayan ki aur mazeed kaha ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daant se kaatney waley se kaha : ''agar chaho to apna haath uskey munh mein dey do , wo bhi usi tarah kaatey jaisey ke tum ne kaata tha aur tum bhi apna haath khinch lena .''gharaz ye ki aapney uskey daanton ki diyat zaya qarar di."
4586,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aisey hi tabeeb bin kar ilaj karey aur tabaabat aur ilaj muaalije mein mashhoor na ho to wo zimmedar hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ye sirf Waleed bin Muslim ki riwayat hai, hamen maloom nahin ke sahih hai ya nahin."
4587,"Janab Abdul-Azeez bin umr bin Abdul-Azeez se riwayat hai ke eik wafad ke log jo merey walid ke paas aaye they un mein se eik ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo muaalij kisi qom mein tabeeb bana phirta ho, jabke us se pehley wo ilm tibb mein maroof na ho aur kisi ka nuqsan kar dey to wo zimmedar hai.'' Abdul-Azeez ne kaha : ye zamanat dawa bataaney mein nahin balke ye rag kaatney , chira deney ya dagh deney ki soorat mein hai."
4588,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne . . . . baqaul Musaddad Fateh waley din khutba irshad farmaya phir Suleman bin Harb aur Musaddad dono apney bayan mein muttafiq hain. . . . . aapney farmaya : '' khabrdar ! tehqiq jahiliyat ke daur ki fakhr ki her baat khoon se mutalliq ho ya maal sey, jiska zikr kya jata ho ya daawa kya jata ho, wo merey qadmon taley ( rondi ja rahi) hai siwaye hajiyon ko pani pilaney aur Baitullah ki khidmat ke amal ke.'' (wo pehley ki tarah bahaal hai. ( phir farmaya : '' khabrdar ! qatle-khata jo amad ke mushabeh ho saantey ya lathi waghera se jaisey bhi ho, uski diyat so oont hai, un mein chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey peton mein bachey hon."
4589,Wuhaib ne Khalid se isi sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya.
4590,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke faqir logon ka eik ghulam tha, usney ameer logon ke eik ghulam ka kaan kaat diya ye ( ameer ( log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas muqadma ley aaye to doosron ne jawab diya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham log faqir hain, to aapney un par koi chiz na dali ."
4591,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi balwe mein maara jaey (aur qatil dekha na gaya ho (ke unki aapas mein sangbaari hui ho ya saantey dandey bazi to uski diyat qatl khata wali hogi . aur jo amadan yaani jaan-bojh kar qatl kya gaya ho to us mein qatil ki jaan se qisaas hai aur jo koi us (qisaas leney) mein aadey aaye to us par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam logon ki lanat ho."
4592,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( janwer ka ( laat maar dena zaya hai. aur ma'dani kaan (ka nuqsan ( zaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke janwer ka Malik us par Sawar ho aur wo laat maar dey ( to zaya hai. ("
4593,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey they, aapney farmaya : '' janwer ka zakhmi kar dena, ma'dani kaan mein hadisa ho jana ya kunwen mein gir padna sab zaya hain aur agar kisi ko koi dafina miley to us mein khums hai.'' ( paanchwan hissey ada karna sharae haq hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain janwer jab bhag gaya ho aur uskey sath koi na ho aur ye hadisa din ke waqt hua ho raat mein na hua ho."
4594,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aag ( se honey wala nuqsan ( zaya hai.''"
4595,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan Rabeyyi ne eik aurat ka daant tod diya to wo log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aagey . pas aapney Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq qisaas ka faisla farmaya. Anas bin Nazar kehney lagey : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! aaj uska daant nahin toda jaeyga . aapney farmaya : '' Anas ! kitabullah ka faisla qisaas hai.'' chunanche doosrey log diyat qubul kar leney par razi ho gaey (aur badla nahin liya ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bada tajjub hua aur farmaya : ''Allah ke kuch bandey aisey bhi hotey hain jo Allah par qasam dal den to wo puri farma deta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, un se puchha gaya ke daant ka qisaas kaisey liya jaey ? to unhoney kaha : ''usey ragad diya jaey.''"
